### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/health

### Login (admin)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### POS Menu (replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/pos/menu
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Public menu (replace QR_TOKEN from seed output)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/public/menu?token=QR_TOKEN

### Daily report
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/admin/reports/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
